items.title: Tesla Model X vs Tesla Model Y: which Tesla SUV should you buy?
items.author: Rob Clymo
items.excerpt: What to look for if you're in the market a Tesla SUV
items.summary: Tesla is gradually filling every spot in the current carbuying marketplace. There's even a budget level compact on the way that'll open up the brand to more customers. It's also establishing itself in the burgeoning SUV sector with models in the shape of the older Tesla Model X and the new Tesla Model Y. Both offer the classic SUV experience while blending it with Tesla's unique styling, dazzling performance and lots of innovation.With demand for SUV's still high, the Tesla Model X is perfect fo
